##########################################################################
##									##
##  RiscOS font data, for mapping a Draw file font name to a platform	##
##  font.								##
##									##
##  Format of this file:						##
##									##
##    riscosname   fontname[,fontname...]   [adjusth adjustv]		##
##									##
##  riscosname	RiscOS font name, or one of the special names "SYSTEM"	##
##		or "DEFAULT".						##
##									##
##  fontname	Platform font name, or a list of alternatives tried	##
##		in order.						##
##									##
##  adjusth	Horizontal adjustment factor, multiplier for font	##
##		width to hopefully achieve the same metrics as the	##
##		original RiscOS font.  Not currently implemented,	##
##		except for the "SYSTEM" font.				##
##									##
##  adjustv	Vertical adjustment factor.  As above, but not		##
##		currently implemented at all.				##
##									##
##  All font name comparisons are case insensitive.			##
##									##
##########################################################################
